hands_on_practices.solution:
我们求解总传播时间
$$T=\int_{r_0}^{r_f}\frac{dr}{v_{\rm rad}(r)},$$  
其中在日心坐标系中
$$v_{\rm rad}(r)=v_{sw}+v_{A,r}(r).$$  
1.  径向 Alfvén 速度：
$$v_{A,r}(r)=\frac{B_r(r)}{\sqrt{\mu_0\,\rho(r)}}\,. $$  
由于
$$B_r(r)=B_{r0}\Bigl(\frac{r_0}{r}\Bigr)^2,\qquad 
\rho(r)=\rho_0\Bigl(\frac{r_0}{r}\Bigr)^2,$$ 
并定义 $v_{A0}=B_{r0}/\sqrt{\mu_0\rho_0}$，可以得到
$$v_{A,r}(r)
=\frac{B_{r0}(r_0/r)^2}{\sqrt{\mu_0\rho_0}(r_0/r)}
=v_{A0}\frac{r_0}{r}\,. $$  
2.  因此
$$\frac{dr}{dt}
=v_{sw}+v_{A0}\frac{r_0}{r}
\quad\Longrightarrow\quad
dt=\frac{dr}{v_{sw}+v_{A0}r_0/r}
=\frac{dr}{v_{sw}\Bigl(1+\frac{v_{A0}r_0}{v_{sw}\,r}\Bigr)}\!. $$  
3.  令 $a=\frac{v_{A0}r_0}{v_{sw}}$。那么
$$T
=\frac{1}{v_{sw}}\int_{r_0}^{r_f}\frac{dr}{1+a/r}
=\frac{1}{v_{sw}}\int_{r_0}^{r_f}\frac{r}{r+a}\,dr
=\frac{1}{v_{sw}}\int_{r_0}^{r_f}\Bigl(1-\frac{a}{r+a}\Bigr)dr.$$  
4.  计算积分：
$$\int_{r_0}^{r_f}1\,dr=r_f-r_0,\qquad
\int_{r_0}^{r_f}\frac{dr}{r+a}
=\ln\frac{r_f+a}{r_0+a}\,. $$  
因此
$$T
=\frac{r_f-r_0}{v_{sw}}
-\frac{a}{v_{sw}}\ln\frac{r_f+a}{r_0+a}
=\frac{r_f-r_0}{v_{sw}}
-\frac{v_{A0}r_0}{v_{sw}^2}
\ln\frac{r_f+\frac{v_{A0}r_0}{v_{sw}}}
     {r_0+\frac{v_{A0}r_0}{v_{sw}}}\,. $$
